慰勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a89645c80b33fe070ae57480bc5ec1383c0989","tid":1777588,"uid":117585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"真係屌佢老母"},{"pid":"5306dba0ca2e7bed09ecc99069dbc474dfbfda49","tid":1777588,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>工聯會中人接受查詢時表示</strong></span></span>，林太會面上說，會委任落選建制議員擔任地區分區委員會、防火委員會、撲滅罪行委員會等公職。該人稱，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>這些位置沒酬金，「絕對無話委任落選者入政府，感覺不到有咩益我們」</strong></span></span>。該人又謂，很多成員正思考未來生計，相信並不覬覦這些公職。在區會落敗的工聯會立法會議員陸頌雄表示，林太沒列出可以選擇的公職，他形容「講得好虛」，又認為林太是真心誠意致歉。在元朗宏逸爭取連任失敗的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>工聯會姚國威</strong></span></span>前日沒與特首見面，他稱不少公職是義工，現時當務之急是為自己找生計。他說暫未決定會否出席21日的茶敘，批評會面的目的不清晰，笑言<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>「特首約我們見工可能會去，但請我們飲啖茶就免」</strong></span></span>。</blockquote><a href=\"https://is.gd/fWa9GF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FfWa9GF&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cRY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=c5a529bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/fWa9GF</a><br />\n柒婆想用啲義務吹水會公職安慰少數派失業議員!? 睇撚咗人地點諗先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d08a63d3e23daadff989a30e697eff7ca3d8f01","tid":1777588,"uid":185565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:48:07.000Z","msg":"火水之母"}]}